videos.description: Bradley Beal attacks his defender off the dribble and gets tough shot to go while being fouled.

videos.headline: Beal hits shot as he's falling down for and-1

videos.description: Bradley Beal shakes his defender and hits a tough fade away at the elbow.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beal knocks down the smooth jumper) 2020/12/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beal knocks down the smooth jumper

videos.description: Wizards' Thomas Bryant throws down the dunk, the only problem is he did it on his own basket giving two points to the Magic.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wizards’ Bryant dunks it … on his own team) 2020/12/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wizards' Bryant dunks it ... on his own team

videos.description: Russell Westbrook falls down while Aaron Gordon backs him down, leaving him wide open for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook slips, leaving Gordon open for dunk) 2020/12/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook slips, leaving Gordon open for dunk

videos.description: Markelle Fultz comes off the screen and throws the lob to Aaron Gordon who flushes it with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Fultz goes up top to Gordon for dunk) 2020/12/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fultz goes up top to Gordon for dunk

videos.description: Markelle Fultz gets into the lane and throws the amazing no-look pass to a cutting Nikola Vucevic for the easy layup.

videos.headline: Fultz drops no-look behind-the-back dime to Vucevic for layup

videos.description: Bradley Beal shows out with 39 points and backcourt mate Russell Westbrook gets his second triple-double in as many games, but it wasn't enough as the Wizards fall to the Magic.

videos.headline: Beal's 39, Westbrook triple-double not enough to propel Wizards

videos.description: Markelle Fultz puts on a show with 21 points and seven assists in the Magic's win over the Wizards.
